                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">Prosecuted.</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">WILLIAM ROS</hi>. (<hi rend="italic">Policeman G</hi> 272). On 20th May I was in Ray Street, Clerkenwell—I saw the prisoner and another boy on some ruins, throwing stones on the railway—I saw the smoke—the prisoner threw a stone at the train, and I took him in custody—the other one jumped over a hoarding seven feet high and got away.</p>
